3.5.	Modelling Strategy
Model	Use Case	Pros	Cons
Logistic Regression 	 Baseline interpretable 	 Fast, explainable 	 Lower accuracy 
Random Forest 	 Feature importance 	 Handles non-linearity 	 Less interpretable 
XGBoost 	 Primary model 	 Best for imbalance, high accuracy 	 Tuning needed 
Isolation Forest 	 Anomaly detection 	 Finds rare patterns 	 Not for probability 

Handling Class Imbalance: SMOTE (Synthetic Minority Oversampling Technique) + Class weight
3.6.	Evaluation Metrics
Metric	Business Significance
Precision 	 When alerting, how often correct? (Reduce false alarms) 
Recall 	 What % of actual incidents caught? (Don't miss incidents) 
F1-Score 	 Balance of precision & recall 
AUC-ROC 	 Overall model discrimination
Business Cost Matrix 	 Cost of false negative > false positive

